00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.730
You see what I'm saying?

00:05:08.730 --> 00:05:13.690
I'm just anticipating,
that the exact solution

00:05:13.690 --> 00:05:14.850
will-- Let's see.

00:05:14.850 --> 00:05:18.820
Something happened at 1/3 and
