00:51:26.150 --> 00:51:33.140
Then what is A transpose w?

00:51:33.140 --> 00:51:34.800
Specifically.

00:51:34.800 --> 00:51:39.010
What am I getting out of it?

00:51:39.010 --> 00:51:43.860
What do I get from here?

