00:52:09.340 --> 00:52:11.100
And what's the name?

00:52:11.100 --> 00:52:15.550
So this is minus the what of w?

00:52:15.550 --> 00:52:20.470
Just tell me, what's
the name everybody uses

00:52:20.470 --> 00:52:22.890
